WEBVTT

00:06.083 --> 00:08.620
Up in the Pyrenees,

00:08.625 --> 00:10.616
there's about as pretty a patch
of country

00:10.625 --> 00:12.081
as you could ever hope to see.

00:12.083 --> 00:15.621
Peaceful forests, raging rivers,

00:15.625 --> 00:18.082
and Basque mountain men
who've been feudin'

00:18.083 --> 00:19.072
with France or Spain

00:19.083 --> 00:22.075
for as long as anyone can remember.

00:22.083 --> 00:24.620
Now and then,
an American tourist gets caught

00:25.125 --> 00:27.116
in the middle of one of
these private wars,

00:27.125 --> 00:30.117
and that's when I
usually get a call.

00:30.125 --> 00:33.117
When somebody's in trouble
and needs some rescuing.

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
